==Development==
''Ewoks'' 1 was written by David Manak, penciled by Warren Kremer, inked by Marie Severin, and published by [[Star Comics]], an imprint of [[Marvel Comics]]. It had a shipping date of [[January 8]], [[1985]] and an on-sale date of [[January 29]], 1985. It was marked with a retail price of US $0.65 and a [[May]] cover date.<ref name="Marvel Age" /> In [[2019]], the issue was reprinted by Marvel as a part of the ''True Believers'' program, with a suggested retail price of US $1.<ref name="Marvel">{{Marvel|url=comics/issue/76285/true_believers_star_wars_-_ewoks_2019_1|text=True Believers: Star Wars - Ewoks (2019) #1}}</ref>

